{
  "video_id": "T_P1D_H1et8",
  "title": "How Jeff Bezos Became the King of E-Commerce",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 130.0,
      "end_time": 5600.0,
      "text": "In 1994, a young, Wall Street hotshot named Jeff Bezos was at a crossroads in his career:"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 5600.0,
      "end_time": 7399.0,
      "text": "Continue amassing a small fortune..."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 7400.0,
      "end_time": 10500.0,
      "text": "...or abandon it all to sell books?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 10500.0,
      "end_time": 13260.0,
      "text": "That decision would single-handedly change the history of e-commerce,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 13260.0,
      "end_time": 17200.0,
      "text": "publishing, film, TV,  journalism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 17200.0,
      "end_time": 20990.0,
      "text": "and quite possibly interstellar travel."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 20990.0,
      "end_time": 22960.0,
      "text": "That decision also represents a recurring theme in his life:"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 22960.0,
      "end_time": 24619.0,
      "text": "Never settle."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 24619.0,
      "end_time": 25698.0,
      "text": "Ever."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 25699.0,
      "end_time": 28429.0,
      "text": "This is how Jeff Bezos took a simple idea into a garage"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 28429.0,
      "end_time": 31840.0,
      "text": "and built one of the largest marketplaces on the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 32780.0,
      "end_time": 35710.0,
      "text": "Jeff Bezos was born on January 12, 1964."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 35710.0,
      "end_time": 38560.0,
      "text": "As a child, he turned his parents' garage"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 38560.0,
      "end_time": 40300.0,
      "text": "into a laboratory for his inventions."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 40780.0,
      "end_time": 44511.0,
      "text": "In his 1982 valedictorian speech, he discussed colonizing outer space"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 44520.0,
      "end_time": 47600.0,
      "text": "and turning Earth into a giant nature preserve."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 47760.0,
      "end_time": 50000.0,
      "text": "Graduating from Princeton with a computer science degree,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 50000.0,
      "end_time": 51520.0,
      "text": "instead of going straight into tech,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 51620.0,
      "end_time": 53300.0,
      "text": "he had other ideas..."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 55580.0,
      "end_time": 59160.0,
      "text": "You don't become a billionaire unless you have this insatiable desire"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 59160.0,
      "end_time": 61328.0,
      "text": "to accrue wealth and power."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 61329.0,
      "end_time": 63640.0,
      "text": "But I think he just looks at it in a way that's"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 63640.0,
      "end_time": 66100.0,
      "text": "really different to almost anyone else I follow."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 66100.0,
      "end_time": 67399.0,
      "text": "That's Tom Metcalf..."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 67420.0,
      "end_time": 69479.0,
      "text": "I'm a billionaires reporter for Bloomberg News."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 69479.0,
      "end_time": 73270.0,
      "text": "He's always driven by success, and Wall Street was the pinnacle for most graduates."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 73270.0,
      "end_time": 75780.0,
      "text": "He was a very mathematical graduate."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 75780.0,
      "end_time": 79270.0,
      "text": "It really fit in his almost quant-like outlook."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 79270.0,
      "end_time": 80940.0,
      "text": "He quickly made a name for himself."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 80940.0,
      "end_time": 85479.0,
      "text": "At 26, the youngest-ever Vice President of Bankers Trust Company."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 85479.0,
      "end_time": 89979.0,
      "text": "At 28, the youngest-ever Senior Vice President of DE Shaw and Co."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 89980.0,
      "end_time": 92800.0,
      "text": "It was there that he discovered a giant, untapped resource:"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 92980.0,
      "end_time": 93740.0,
      "text": "the internet."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 93920.0,
      "end_time": 98320.0,
      "text": "He was seeing the internet grow by 2300% a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 98400.0,
      "end_time": 100180.0,
      "text": "In all his time at a Wall Street firm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 100180.0,
      "end_time": 102660.0,
      "text": "he'd never seen such a growth opportunity."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 102920.0,
      "end_time": 105280.0,
      "text": "He went through a whole list of industries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 105280.0,
      "end_time": 106540.0,
      "text": "and, if you think about books,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 106540.0,
      "end_time": 108390.0,
      "text": "easy to package. Hard to damage."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 108390.0,
      "end_time": 110679.0,
      "text": "And of course the internet offers an infinite library."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 110679.0,
      "end_time": 112429.0,
      "text": "DE Shaw did not share his optimism."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 112429.0,
      "end_time": 114360.0,
      "text": "For the opportunity of a lifetime,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 114360.0,
      "end_time": 116240.0,
      "text": "Bezos would have to leave Wall Street."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 117340.0,
      "end_time": 119800.0,
      "text": "Whatever it is that you want to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 119800.0,
      "end_time": 121740.0,
      "text": "there's gonna be risk in your life."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 121740.0,
      "end_time": 124470.0,
      "text": "And risk is a necessary component of progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 124470.0,
      "end_time": 126120.0,
      "text": "And he quite simply packed his stuff up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 126120.0,
      "end_time": 127900.0,
      "text": "drove across the country."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 127900.0,
      "end_time": 130800.0,
      "text": "And the legend goes that, while in the car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 130800.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132240.0,
      "text": "he was writing the business plans."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 132250.0,
      "end_time": 134520.0,
      "text": "Setting up shop in his garage, in 1994,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 134520.0,
      "end_time": 136800.0,
      "text": "he incorporated his book company under the name…."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 138340.0,
      "end_time": 139200.0,
      "text": "“Cadabra”."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 139200.0,
      "end_time": 142700.0,
      "text": "It wasn't great when a lawyer misheard it as \"cadaver\"."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 143260.0,
      "end_time": 145700.0,
      "text": "He ultimately landed on \"Amazon\" for a couple reasons."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 145700.0,
      "end_time": 147440.0,
      "text": "Firstly, the name beginning with 'A'"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 147440.0,
      "end_time": 150100.0,
      "text": "would likely be on top of any alphabetized web search."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 150240.0,
      "end_time": 153380.0,
      "text": "And he kind of liked the fact that it tied into the world's largest river,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 153380.0,
      "end_time": 156690.0,
      "text": "and he was setting up plans to make Amazon the world's largest company."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 156690.0,
      "end_time": 158440.0,
      "text": "Launching in July 1995,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 158440.0,
      "end_time": 159859.0,
      "text": "a bell was installed to ring"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 159860.0,
      "end_time": 161170.0,
      "text": "every time a book was sold."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 161170.0,
      "end_time": 163417.0,
      "text": "In its first month, Amazon sold to people"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 163418.0,
      "end_time": 165830.0,
      "text": "in all 50 states and 45 different countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 165830.0,
      "end_time": 167340.0,
      "text": "The bell was gone in weeks."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 167340.0,
      "end_time": 168340.0,
      "text": "All their expectations were smashed."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 168340.0,
      "end_time": 170880.0,
      "text": "They thought they'd maybe sell dozens of books the first week."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 171000.0,
      "end_time": 171960.0,
      "text": "It was in fact hundreds."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 171960.0,
      "end_time": 172960.0,
      "text": "Then thousands."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 172960.0,
      "end_time": 174630.0,
      "text": "And, of course today, millions."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 174630.0,
      "end_time": 176140.0,
      "text": "By September 1995,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 176140.0,
      "end_time": 179510.0,
      "text": "Amazon processed $20,000 in monthly sales."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 179510.0,
      "end_time": 181299.0,
      "text": "With its 1997 IPO,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 181300.0,
      "end_time": 183880.0,
      "text": "Amazon was valued at $400 million."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 183880.0,
      "end_time": 187160.0,
      "text": "By 1999, Jeff Bezos was worth $10 billion"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 187160.0,
      "end_time": 189240.0,
      "text": "and was Time's Man of the Year."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 189240.0,
      "end_time": 192240.0,
      "text": "But soon after, the dot com crash had people skeptical:"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 192240.0,
      "end_time": 194170.0,
      "text": "was Amazon a sustainable business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 194170.0,
      "end_time": 195760.0,
      "text": "or would the bubble burst?"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 196920.0,
      "end_time": 201619.0,
      "text": "Anyone who's met Bezos knows he's extraordinarily charismatic and very convincing."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 201720.0,
      "end_time": 202940.0,
      "text": "In terms of the long-term vision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 202940.0,
      "end_time": 205300.0,
      "text": "he had it mapped out for decades."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 205300.0,
      "end_time": 206540.0,
      "text": "Whatever happened in the short term,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 206540.0,
      "end_time": 208790.0,
      "text": "he wasn't going to change that plan."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 208340.0,
      "end_time": 209880.0,
      "text": "And I think he conveyed that pretty well"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 209880.0,
      "end_time": 211000.0,
      "text": "to his stockholders."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 211000.0,
      "end_time": 213320.0,
      "text": "With the crash eliminating many competitors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 213320.0,
      "end_time": 215470.0,
      "text": "Amazon strengthened its grip on the market"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 215470.0,
      "end_time": 217109.0,
      "text": "and expanded beyond books."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 217110.0,
      "end_time": 218110.0,
      "text": "The Kindle."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 218110.0,
      "end_time": 219110.0,
      "text": "Alexa."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 219110.0,
      "end_time": 220110.0,
      "text": "Amazon Studios."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 220110.0,
      "end_time": 221110.0,
      "text": "And of course…."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 221110.0,
      "end_time": 222140.0,
      "text": "Amazon Prime."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 222140.0,
      "end_time": 224679.0,
      "text": "What it does is it really locks people into the Amazon ecosystem."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 224680.0,
      "end_time": 227300.0,
      "text": "They're much more inclined to be buying a lot more."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 227300.0,
      "end_time": 228430.0,
      "text": "Word of mouth spreads."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 228430.0,
      "end_time": 233800.0,
      "text": "And that has been the biggest driver of Amazon's incredible revenue growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 233800.0,
      "end_time": 236340.0,
      "text": "Yet, historically, Amazon has seen modest annual profits."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 236340.0,
      "end_time": 239140.0,
      "text": "There's an enormous amount of cash flowing through the company."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 239140.0,
      "end_time": 242179.0,
      "text": "And what Bezos does - he's not returning that to shareholders."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 242180.0,
      "end_time": 243700.0,
      "text": "He's reinvesting that in the company."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 243700.0,
      "end_time": 245140.0,
      "text": "For sure in its core businesses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 245140.0,
      "end_time": 248319.0,
      "text": "but also going off for these almost moonshot projects."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 248319.0,
      "end_time": 250119.0,
      "text": "My vision for Blue Origin is"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 250120.0,
      "end_time": 253510.0,
      "text": "millions of people living and working in space."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 253510.0,
      "end_time": 255000.0,
      "text": "This is such a game-changer."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 255000.0,
      "end_time": 256450.0,
      "text": "Amazon to buy Whole Foods."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 256450.0,
      "end_time": 259740.0,
      "text": "Jeff Bezos is now the richest person in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 259740.0,
      "end_time": 264120.0,
      "text": "$250 million for the storied Washington Post."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 264130.0,
      "end_time": 266983.0,
      "text": "His acquisition of the Washington Post not only raised eyebrows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 266983.0,
      "end_time": 269430.0,
      "text": "but put him at odds with another well-known billionaire."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 269430.0,
      "end_time": 273430.0,
      "text": "He bought the Washington Post to have political influence."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 273430.0,
      "end_time": 274740.0,
      "text": "If I become President,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 274740.0,
      "end_time": 275750.0,
      "text": "oh do they have problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 275750.0,
      "end_time": 277380.0,
      "text": "They're going to have such problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 278120.0,
      "end_time": 281159.0,
      "text": "Bezos and Trump are probably as different as two entrepreneurs can get."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 281159.0,
      "end_time": 283980.0,
      "text": "Trump is pretty reactionary, kind of emotional,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 283980.0,
      "end_time": 286320.0,
      "text": "whereas Bezos normally doesn't really respond."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 286320.0,
      "end_time": 287700.0,
      "text": "Though once he did suggest"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 287700.0,
      "end_time": 289979.0,
      "text": "he'd be willing to send Donald Trump into space."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 289980.0,
      "end_time": 291200.0,
      "text": "And, you know, I have a rocket company so..."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 291200.0,
      "end_time": 292920.0,
      "text": "the capability is there."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 292930.0,
      "end_time": 295640.0,
      "text": "Few businessmen choose to make an enemy of a president."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 295640.0,
      "end_time": 298140.0,
      "text": "But having built an empire out of a garage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 298140.0,
      "end_time": 300600.0,
      "text": "Jeff Bezos has proven capable"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 300600.0,
      "end_time": 301660.0,
      "text": "of handling any adversary."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 301660.0,
      "end_time": 303580.0,
      "text": "Especially complacency."
    }
  ]
}